ncial-services`, `/industries/banking`, `/industries/insurance`, etc.\n    *   **Transformation Tools**: `/build/blueprint`, `/contact` (though currently maps to `/page.tsx#contact` but may require static page routes).\n    *   **Legal / Information**: `/privacy`, `/nda`, `/terms`, `/careers`, `/investors`, etc.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Homepage Gaps\n*   **Presence of Required Sections**: The landing page (`components/LandingPage.tsx`) contains all 11 required sections:\n    1.  **Hero** (`HeroSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    2.  **Enterprise Quick Search** (`QuickSearchSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    3.  **Garage Foundry Factory journey** (`JourneySection.tsx`) — Present.\n    4.  **What We Build** (`WhatWeBuildSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    5.  **Interactive Experience** (`InteractiveExperienceSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    6.  **Global Presence** (`GlobalPresenceSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    7.  **Client Success** (`ClientSuccessSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    8.  **Live Dashboard** (`LiveDashboardSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    9.  **Latest Research** (`LatestResearchSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    10. **Contact** (`ContactSection.tsx`) — Present.\n    11. **Footer** (`Footer.tsx`) — Present.\n*   **Extra/Approved Sections**: The landing page also renders several approved high-end sections:\n    *   `TalkToAgentSection.tsx`\n    *   `BuildAIEnterpriseSection.tsx` (interactive Blueprint generator)\n    *   `FoundrySection.tsx`\n    *   `IndustrySolutionsSection.tsx`\n    *   `InsightsSection.tsx`\n    *   `GarageSection.tsx`\n*   **Homepage Section Gaps/Dead Imports**:\n    *   `ProductizedAssetsSection.tsx` is imported in `components/LandingPage.tsx` but is **not rendered** in the JSX. This is a dead import that can be safely left alone or cleaned up.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Design-System Observations\n*   **Framework**: Next.js App Router (v16.2.9) with React 19.2.4.\n*   **Styling Stack**: Tailwind CSS v4 is configured (`\"tailwindcss\": \"^4\"`, `\"@tailwindcss/postcss\": \"^4\"`). Tra